{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:0","text":"RenderMan for Maya 可以在字符串参数中替换若干预定义 tokens（标记）。它们可用于动画纹理序列、引用特定存储位置等。"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:1","text":"Token（标记）"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:2","text":"Meaning（含义）"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:3","text":"<scene>"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:4","text":"场景名称"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:5","text":"<layer>"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:6","text":"Maya Render Layer 名称"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:7","text":"<camera>"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:8","text":"渲染 camera（相机）名称"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:9","text":"<aov>"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:10","text":"AOV 或 LPE 名称"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:11","text":"<aovdir>"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:12","text":"这会将 AOVs 写入具名子目录"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:13","text":"<f4>"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:14","text":"帧号 padding（填充位数），此例为 4；若不需要填充可省略，或使用更小的数字"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:15","text":"<ext>"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:16","text":"文件类型扩展名"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:17","text":"<ws>"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:18","text":"Maya 当前 workspace（工作区），即项目中的文件路径"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:19","text":"<version>"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:20","text":"插入上方指定的 version（版本）编号"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:21","text":"<take>"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:22","text":"插入上方指定的 take（拍摄/分次）编号"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:23","text":"<date>"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:24","text":"Current date（当前日期）"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:25","text":"<assetlib>"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:26","text":"标准 RenderMan Asset Library 的 Path（路径）"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:27","text":"<file>"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:28","text":"场景文件名"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:29","text":"<frame>"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:30","text":"十进制帧号"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:31","text":"<jobid>"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:32","text":"唯一 job（作业）identifier（标识符）"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:33","text":"<shape>"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:34","text":"短 shape 名称（所有实例具有相同的 shape 名称）"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:35","text":"<shapepath>"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:36","text":"长 shape 名称（所有实例都有唯一的"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:37","text":"shapepath 名称）"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:38","text":"<time>"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:39","text":"Current time（当前时间）"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:40","text":"<udim>"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:41","text":"UDIM identifier（标识符，仅在渲染时替换）"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:42","text":"<imagedir>"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:43","text":"此项包含完整的图像输出目录"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:44","text":"_MAPID_"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:45","text":"Generic texture atlas identifier（通用纹理图集标识符）"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:46","text":"（仅在渲染时替换）"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:47","text":"Environment Variables（环境变量）"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:48","text":"环境变量必须以 $ 符号开头，并且只能使用大写字母、数字和 \"_\" 字符："}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:49","text":"：返回 txmake 工具的路径。"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:50","text":"也可以使用 curly braces（花括号）进行组合："}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:51","text":"Retrieving attribute values（检索属性值）"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:52","text":"RfM 不再支持 TCL 表达式，但允许进行 attribute evaluation（属性求值）："}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:53","text":"返回 shape 节点上 'time' 属性的值（这里是 'shape' 节点，而不是 'transform' 节点）。"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:54","text":"也可以通过指定 formatting string（格式化字符串）来格式化数值属性值："}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:55","text":"：如果 time 的值为"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:56","text":"，则会返回"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:57","text":"。"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:58","text":"这里使用"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:59","text":"Python 的标准格式说明符"}
{"item_id":"a1374ebe46:60","text":"。"}
